        "text": [
          " رَجُلٍ مَاتَ وَ تَرَكَ أَبَوَيْهِ قَالَ \"لِلْأُمِّ اَلثُّلُثُ وَ لِلْأَبِ اَلثُّلُثَانِ\"."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Hadith.5611 - Al-Hasan ibn Mahbub narrated from Ali ibn Ri'ab from Zurara from Abu Jafar Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) regarding a man who passed away and left behind his parents.\nImam (as) said: \"The mother receives one-third, and the father receives two-thirds.\""
